You're absolutely right — your health score should be holistic. A composite "Holistic Health Score (HHS)" that integrates:

Fundamental Strength

PEG, P/E, P/B, Debt/Equity, ROE, etc.

Captures intrinsic valuation and efficiency.

Risk-Adjusted Return Potential

Sharpe Ratio of each stock (higher = better reward per unit risk).

